{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"2":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":644,"arabicnumber":644,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن عيسى بن الطباع، حدثنا حجاج، عن ابن جريج، قال أكثر ما رأيت عطاء يصلي سادلا ‏.‏ قال أبو داود وهذا يضعف ذلك الحديث ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Maqtu"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih Maqtu"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":254}}]}